<h1>Olimey AI AI System Prompt</h1>
<h2>Complete Agent Instructions Reference Document</h2>
<p><br><br></p>
<p><strong>Document Type:</strong> System Prompt Specification</p>
<p><strong>Agent:</strong> Olimey AI (Source of Wealth Assessment)</p>
<p><strong>Platform:</strong> Olimey AI</p>
<p><strong>Version:</strong> Current Production</p>
<p><strong>Date:</strong> 16 March 2026</p>
<p><strong>Classification:</strong> Internal — Confidential</p>
<p><br><br></p>
<p style="font-size:10pt;color:#a0aec0;">This document contains the complete system prompt used by the Olimey AI AI agent when performing Source of Wealth assessments. It includes the core agent prompt, universal guardrails, and the knowledge base ingestion directive.</p>
</div>

